reviews.text: Used to be good. Quality noticeably declined. Lunch set was just ok. The HK$2xx steak for dinner was terrible.
Had the steak there.  Decor and ambiance is good and the steaks are good properly.  The fries/chips are crispy and properly salted.
Affordable and yummy foods
Ok

Ordered pork neck lunch set and took 30 mins to come while my colleagues had already got theirs in 10mins. It wasn't even that busy at the time. When it finally came, there was only a few slices of pork ... This added more to my disappointment. They didn't ask what soup we wanted either. No tip for them and not going back!

reviews.text: 第一次食，食品質素可以，但服務欠佳!問是否跟湯?侍應只簡單一句答:得一款!(其實可以加多句話比食客知是日餐湯是甚麽)。上餐時未收湯碟，餐碟要食客先接，她才有手收湯碟! 由點餐、埋單、找錢直至離開都聽不到一句多謝(多謝、bye bye是服務業的基本吧)反而我對侍應説了幾次唔該
食物有水準, 員工有禮貌, 但坐位狹窄
一般，侍應服務差，午餐時等待收拾枱面，第一次見侍應要坐在客人的椅上執枱及擺餐具，可說是奇景
